WEBVTT

00:10:29.524 --> 00:10:31.870
right before the event happened.

00:10:31.870 --> 00:10:34.364
Bia started a campaign, and we even watched

00:10:34.364 --> 00:10:37.747
her school 24/7 through webcam monitoring,

00:10:37.747 --> 00:10:39.761
and many months afterwards,

00:10:39.761 --> 00:10:41.392
the government changed their minds.

00:10:41.392 --> 00:10:44.316
Bia's school stayed in place.

00:10:44.316 --> 00:10:46.487
There's also Jovita.

00:10:46.487 --> 00:10:48.759
She's an amazing woman whose daughter

00:10:48.759 --> 00:10:51.420
went missing about 10 years ago,

00:10:51.420 --> 00:10:53.855
and since then, she has been looking

00:10:53.855 --> 00:10:55.039
for her daughter.

00:10:55.039 --> 00:10:57.815
In that process, she found out

00:10:57.815 --> 00:11:00.368
that first, she was not alone.